	"<div class=\"slide slide-72 master-content\">\n<div class=\"slide-wrapper \">\n\t\n<h1>Grunt.next Goals</h1>\n\n\n<h2><a href=\"https://cowboy.github.io/state-of-grunt-fe-summit-2014-talk/#55\" target=\"_blank\">The State of Grunt August 2014</a></h2>\n\n\n<div class=\"slide-content\">\n\t<!-- slide-content -->\n\n<ul>\n<li>More modular and maintainable</li>\n<li>Support existing 0.4.x plugins via optional adapter, &amp; support Gulp &amp; Broccoli plugins</li>\n<li>Tasks support stream-based and promise-based input/output</li>\n<li>Support tasks &amp; pipelines that can run in series or parallel</li>\n<li>All Grunt tasks and file I/O will be async (under the hood)</li>\n</ul>\n<!-- /slide-content -->\n</div>\n\t<footer>\n\t\t<span class=\"presentation-title\">Grunt-ify Your Front-End Web Development</span>\n<span class=\"presentation-pagination\">72</span>\n\n\t</footer>\n</div>\n\n</div>",
